Contact Book Application
A simple Python command-line Contact Book application that lets you manage contacts easily. You can add, view, search, update, and delete contacts with validation for names, phone numbers, and emails.
Features
 Add new contacts with:
  Name
  Phone number (10 digits)
  Email
  Address
 View all saved contacts.
 Search for a contact by name or phone number.
 Update contact details.
 Delete a contact.
 Input validation for name, phone, and email to avoid errors.
